286
00:27:54,910 --> 00:27:57,902
Your hair. Untie it.

287
00:28:37,230 --> 00:28:39,380
Tie it up.

288
00:28:40,910 --> 00:28:43,822
You mean braid it?
You "braid" hair.

289
00:28:47,870 --> 00:28:49,701
Are you sure
you don't want to come?

290
00:28:49,830 --> 00:28:52,549
