291
00:28:52,670 --> 00:28:55,184
I'm going to see him,
not her.

292
00:28:55,590 --> 00:28:59,026
I like it here when
everyone's gone.

293
00:28:59,150 --> 00:29:01,618
At last, I get some privacy.

294
00:29:04,070 --> 00:29:06,823
What, do Sabras
shake hands?

295
00:29:12,870 --> 00:29:16,783
Last one to the gate,
