296
00:29:43,070 --> 00:29:45,220
Is he coming?

297
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:48,944
He said he would come today?

298
00:29:50,150 --> 00:29:51,947
Mama,

299
00:29:52,550 --> 00:29:54,859
I brought you flowers.

300
00:29:55,110 --> 00:30:00,503
I grew them myself.
