301
00:30:00,670 --> 00:30:03,548
Don't talk to her like that,
she's not a little girl.

302
00:30:16,710 --> 00:30:20,180
Do you want to go out
for some fresh air?

303
00:30:25,110 --> 00:30:28,022
You're not dressed warmly
