00:36:01,070 --> 00:36:04,187
Sometimes, memories can kill.

367
00:36:06,910 --> 00:36:09,549
So, how's Yola?
- So how's Sarah B.

368
00:36:11,830 --> 00:36:13,980
You didn't go see
your mother, did you?

369
00:36:14,110 --> 00:36:17,659
