376
00:36:47,110 --> 00:36:49,419
Can I come with you?

377
00:37:14,950 --> 00:37:18,260
It was just by chance, right?

378
00:37:22,430 --> 00:37:26,548
What happened to Yola,

379
00:37:30,150 --> 00:37:35,429
It couldn't happen to
someone else, could it?

