are waiting for you.

452
00:46:43,310 --> 00:46:45,904
My dear children.

453
00:46:46,510 --> 00:46:49,104
I have no words
of comfort.

454
00:46:51,950 --> 00:46:55,181
We all shared
in Yola's joy,

